title: Les Vaux de la Celle
description: An ancient Gallo-Roman sanctuary near modern Genainville (France), with excavated remains of a temple, nymphaeum, and theater: BAtlas 11 B3 Génainville (sic)

properties.description: The site Les Vaux de la Celle is located in the commune Genainville, département Val-d'Oise.
properties.title: Archaeological site Les Vaux de la Celle
